8d4ab838-34b7-4b73-9743-d8ca3f75c3a4.do_description: To make the output, you have to...make vertical line under the point shape ONLY where there is a square under it, with the same color of the square and draw it down to the bottom.
8d4ab838-34b7-4b73-9743-d8ca3f75c3a4.grid_description: The output grid size...remains the same.
8d4ab838-34b7-4b73-9743-d8ca3f75c3a4.see_description: In the input, you should see...an up point shape with different colored squares around it.

b15f5e29-f182-49a9-99b7-2f443a4a29ba.do_description: To make the output, you have to...make vertical lines from the first empty block under the large shape to the very end only on the grid that have a colored block existing already  under the large area.  The color should be the same as the small cubes already there.
b15f5e29-f182-49a9-99b7-2f443a4a29ba.grid_description: The output grid size...stay the same
b15f5e29-f182-49a9-99b7-2f443a4a29ba.see_description: In the input, you should see...an large shape and cubes of a different color

f844bf55-a8ad-4ab8-b0f8-536a79740c75.do_description: To make the output, you have to... Using the color of the random blocks around the outside, make a row straight down from the arrow head figure to meet any colored blocks below, extending the new row to the end of the grid
f844bf55-a8ad-4ab8-b0f8-536a79740c75.grid_description: The output grid size... remains the same
f844bf55-a8ad-4ab8-b0f8-536a79740c75.see_description: In the input, you should see... a shape like the head of an arrow surrounded by black with single blocks of a different color randomly spaced around the outside of the grid.
